                        <interp inst="t18800524-name-451" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTE</persName>
                  </hi>. This half-crown and florin are bad.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoner in hit Statement before the Magistrate and in his Defence said that he received the florin from a lady for carrying a parcel, and that the two men asked him to drink on the Saturday.</hi>
               </p>
